description: This file configures the Remotion video rendering settings by importing the Config object from @remotion/cli and setting specific options such as video image format and output overwrite behavior.

methods.name: setVideoImageFormat
methods.description: Sets the image format for videos generated by Remotion, here configured as 'jpeg'.

methods.name: setOverwriteOutput
methods.description: Configures whether to overwrite existing output files, here set to true.
